    "Text used in MWOs are also much shorter when compared to other text in the NLP corpora, even though they may contain the same number of records (Dima et al., 2021).",
    "MWOs typically consist of a unique identifier, the problem, action taken, and timestamp of when it was created and closed, etc.",
